Class ContestantInformation

java.lang.Object
  muzeyen.ContestantInformation

public class ContestantInformation
extends java.lang.Object

This class holds the information of each contestant. It contains fields for first name, last name, street address (street name and street number), city, province, postal code, phone number and birth date

Author:
Issa Muzeyen, September 21, 2015
